The 10th International Conference on Gravitation and Cosmology: New Horizon and Singularities in Gravity (ICGC 2023)
was hosted by the Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Guwahati, India during December 6 - 9, 2023 organized 
by the Indian Association for General Relativity and Gravitation (IAGRG). Topics covered during this meeting: 
<ul>
  <li>Classical & Quantum Gravity</li>
  <li>Gravitational Waves</li>
  <li>Astrophysical Relativity</li>
  <li>Cosmology</li>
</ul>
